            "title": "Activities of Thiosulphate and 3-Mercaptopyruvate-cyanide-sulphurtransferases in Poultry Birds and the Fruit Bat",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Femi Kayode Agboola",
                    "lastName": "."
